title: IFaxDoc::get_RecipientHomePhone (faxcom.h)
description: Sets or retrieves the RecipientHomePhone property of a FaxDoc object. The RecipientHomePhone property is a null-terminated string that contains the home telephone number of the recipient of the fax transmission. (Get)
